<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 14:06:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“以色列政府意图消灭加沙的巴勒斯坦人”：南非向国际法院提出种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</link><description>尽管以色列通常认为联合国和国际法庭对他们有偏见，但它正在非常认真地对待这些指控，并在哈马斯袭击后部署了一支强大的法律团队来为其军事行动辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/israeli-govt-is-intent-on-destroying-palestinians-south-africa-presents-genocide-case/0000018c-f8bc-d517-af9d-fcbe87ae0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔否认哈马斯领导人流亡条款，以色列回应新的人质释放提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</link><description>政治消息人士强调，以色列的一贯立场不是同意哈马斯停止战争的要求，也不是以完全停止在加沙地带的军事活动为前提达成释放人质协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 13:21:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/qatar-denies-hamas-leaders-clause-as-israel-responds-to-new-hostage-release-proposal/0000018c-f87b-d517-af9d-fc7f5e340000</guid></item><item><title>1986年以来失踪士兵的女儿罗恩·阿拉德：以色列政界人士必须就释放人质进行谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</link><description>尤瓦尔·阿拉德在脸书上写道，“因为历史不仅在我眼前重演，而且人们似乎拒绝从历史中吸取教训”，并警告应立即将人质带回家</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/daughter-of-soldier-missing-since-1986-israel-must-negotiate-for-hostages-release/0000018c-f7d0-d432-a7ae-fff972390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科技行业的情况会变得更糟吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</link><description>去年是初创国家有史以来最糟糕的一年。现在，2024 年将会出现更多战争、腐败政府和持续的全球经济衰退</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 12:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/can-things-get-even-worse-for-israel-tech/0000018c-f860-dd94-a9cc-faecd27d0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人因玩枪误杀朋友而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</link><description>自以色列国家安全部降低申请和领取持枪许可证的条件以来，已发生多起涉枪伤亡事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 10:05:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/three-israelis-arrested-for-accidentally-killing-friend-after-toying-with-gun/0000018c-f796-d365-a3ce-f7f67c720000</guid></item><item><title>枪械如何成为以色列必备的时尚潮流</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，枪支已经从一种防护手段转变为一种身份象征和宣言</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 09:15:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/biggest-fashion-trend-in-israel-in-2024-firearms/0000018c-f3dd-d6ce-abcc-fbdf22600000</guid></item><item><title>“南非是哈马斯的合法机构”：以色列谴责国际法院种族灭绝听证会“扭曲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</link><description>海牙国际法院听取了南非的指控，指控以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝，但未能惩罚煽动种族灭绝的人。检方援引总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡、总统艾萨克·赫尔佐格和以色列部长的声明作为种族灭绝意图的证据。以色列将于周五针对这些指控为自己辩护</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 06:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/intl-court-of-justice-unlikely-to-order-gaza-cease-fire-israeli-officials-say/0000018c-f711-d432-a7ae-fff9faed0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的共和党对手在爱荷华州辩论中就以色列和反犹太主义问题发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</link><description>美国前驻联合国特使尼基·黑利（Nikki Haley）猛烈抨击佛罗里达州州长罗恩·德桑蒂斯（Ron DeSantis）未能充分打击家乡的新纳粹游行和反犹太主义，而德桑蒂斯则指责总统。拜登称美军在中东“任人宰割”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/trumps-republican-rivals-spar-over-israel-antisemitism-at-iowa-debate/0000018c-f6a6-d432-a7ae-ffff81650000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员告诉国土报，世界法院不太可能在加沙种族灭绝听证会上下令停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</link><description>预计以色列将于周五在海牙国际法院对指控提出反驳</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/south-africa-to-present-genocide-case-against-israel-at-world-court-on-thursday/0000018c-f4f8-d3a7-afdf-f5fab49c0000</guid></item><item><title>美国希望建立一个“新的巴勒斯坦权力机构”来统治加沙。作为交换，阿巴斯希望建国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯支持巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯建立巴勒斯坦国的步骤，但华盛顿说服以色列做出让步并不容易，这个问题可能会使其与内塔尼亚胡政府发生冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/u-s-wants-a-new-palestinian-authority-to-rule-gaza-in-exchange-abbas-wants-statehood/0000018c-f527-d365-a3ce-f5f7702d0000</guid></item><item><title>家人通过扩音器向加沙边境哈马斯扣押的以色列人质呼喊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</link><description>以色列高等法院驳回因战争而罢黜内塔尼亚胡的请愿 ■ 以色列挫败了两名东耶路撒冷居民策划的伊斯兰国袭击 ■ 国际法院在海牙举行的种族灭绝听证会今天结束；以色列周五就指控进行辩护 ■ 以色列国防军发现法医证据，证明哈马斯在汗尤尼斯地下新发现的隧道中扣押了人质 ■ 布林肯表示，以色列与该地区合作，开辟通往巴勒斯坦国的道路，将孤立伊朗</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:21:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article-live/ahead-of-world-court-hearing-netanyahu-rejects-calls-for-gaza-population-transfer/0000018c-f676-dd68-a3cf-f6feba5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方以潜在暴力为由取消了特拉维夫犹太-阿拉伯和平抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</link><description>计划在“只有和平才能带来安全”的旗帜下集会的组织者发誓要向最高法院的裁决提出上诉</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/citing-potential-violence-police-nix-jewish-arab-peace-protest-in-tel-aviv/0000018c-f5f6-d432-a7ae-fffffcd40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列未成年人因间谍罪入狱 18 个月。调查显示他是以色列国防军情报人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</link><description>这名当时 17 岁的年轻人被指控发布高度敏感信息，但警方未能按照军方官员的要求彻底调查他的说法。此后经军事情报部门核实，但未告知检方</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:04:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minor-held-for-18-months-for-espionage-before-idf-admitted-controlling-him/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fed5530000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会批准决议要求也门胡塞武装立即停止袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</link><description>安理会还呼吁胡塞武装释放银河领袖号，这是一艘由日本运营的车辆运输公司，与该组织上个月征用的一名以色列商人有联系。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 23:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-11/ty-article/un-security-council-approves-resolution-demanding-yemens-houthis-immediately-end-attacks/0000018c-f5a5-dd68-a3cf-f7af8a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>50 名大屠杀研究人员要求大屠杀纪念馆谴责以色列呼吁在加沙进行种族灭绝的公开言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/holocaust-researchers-to-yad-vashem-condemn-israeli-public-discourse-calling-for-genocide/0000018c-f53b-dd68-a3cf-f7bf04d20000</link><description>研究人员表示，以色列官员和人士所说的“煽动灭绝”“可能达到种族灭绝的阶段”。他们呼吁大屠杀纪念馆吸取大屠杀的教训</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/holocaust-researchers-to-yad-vashem-condemn-israeli-public-discourse-calling-for-genocide/0000018c-f53b-dd68-a3cf-f7bf04d20000</guid></item><item><title>专家如何看待国际法院的以色列加沙种族灭绝案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/how-experts-see-israels-gaza-genocide-case-in-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-f4f3-d365-a3ce-f5f740260000</link><description>“种族灭绝是一个非常高的门槛。一名专家表示，这不足以证明你集体杀人。以色列必须证明其意图是消灭哈马斯而不是巴勒斯坦人民，并且其大声喧哗的立法者可能会说种族灭绝，但没有实际权力这样做</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/how-experts-see-israels-gaza-genocide-case-in-the-international-court-of-justice/0000018c-f4f3-d365-a3ce-f5f740260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列福利官员称政府预算削减将伤害大屠杀幸存者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-welfare-officials-say-govt-budget-cut-would-harm-massacre-survivors/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fee44a0000</link><description>福利部消息人士担心预算削减将达到约 8%，称这对援助撤离人员和弱势群体来说是“致命一击”。阿拉伯当局领导人警告说，估计的削减将严重影响降低犯罪率的努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-welfare-officials-say-govt-budget-cut-would-harm-massacre-survivors/0000018c-f4f8-dd68-a3cf-f6fee44a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公务员的个人信息从政府数据库泄露并被外国实体掌握</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/info-of-israeli-civil-servants-leaked-from-government-database-held-by-foreign-entity/0000018c-f47a-d3a7-afdf-f5fac2000000</link><description>应国家检察官办公室的要求，表面上出于调查该事件的目的，发布了一项禁止媒体报道泄密事件的禁言令。然而，一位专家告诉《国土报》，此类禁言令“主要源于羞耻感，以掩盖他们的失败”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:46:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/info-of-israeli-civil-servants-leaked-from-government-database-held-by-foreign-entity/0000018c-f47a-d3a7-afdf-f5fac2000000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，政客只有在支持的情况下才可以谈论种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-10/ty-article/.highlight/in-israel-politicians-are-allowed-to-talk-about-genocide-only-if-they-support-it/0000018c-f48c-d365-a3ce-f5fef7ce0000</link><description>七十名议员签署了一项动议，驱逐左翼议员奥弗·卡西夫，因为他支持南非针对以色列的种族灭绝案。与此同时，高级部长的声明正在积极破坏以色列的战争努力</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:40:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-10/ty-article/.highlight/in-israel-politicians-are-allowed-to-talk-about-genocide-only-if-they-support-it/0000018c-f48c-d365-a3ce-f5fef7ce0000</guid></item><item><title>战争期间，以色列对巴勒斯坦东耶路撒冷房屋的拆除激增；内盖夫推土工作重新启动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/demolitions-of-palestinian-east-jerusalem-homes-spike-amid-war-negev-bulldozing-renewed/0000018c-f35e-d28a-a1fe-f7fedf170000</link><description>在之前的加沙战争中，当局没有在东耶路撒冷进行拆除活动，以缓解紧张局势。然而，自 10 月份以来，拆毁房屋的速度有所加快，据报道，2023 年被拆除的房屋数量激增了 60%。周三也标志着自战争开始以来，未被承认的贝都因村庄首次被拆除</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 18:24:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-10/ty-article/.premium/demolitions-of-palestinian-east-jerusalem-homes-spike-amid-war-negev-bulldozing-renewed/0000018c-f35e-d28a-a1fe-f7fedf170000</guid></item></channel></rss>